To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private RateOfChangePercent _rocp;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_rocp = ROCP(symbol, period);

// In OnData()
if (_rocp.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "rateofchangepercent", _rocp.Current.Value);
}
